AnnotatedItemContainer<HpoDisease>, Iterable<HpoDisease>, Versioned
public interface HpoDiseases extends AnnotatedItemContainer<HpoDisease>, Versioned
A Versioned container for HpoDiseases with a bunch of convenience methods for getting the individual HpoDiseases.
